</date>
Western Cape, Table Mountain National Park, Table Mountain, mossy pool behind Woodhead Reservoir (abundant); 
<date box="[1140,1260,366,391]" pageId="11" pageNumber="452" value="2011-09-25">
<number box="[1140,1167,366,391]" pageId="11" pageNumber="452" value="25.0">25</number>
